#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:1
msgid "Path planning"
msgstr "路径规划"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:3
msgid ""
"IR-SIM includes grid- and sampling-based path planners for computing a "
"collision-free path on an occupancy map. Planners are used "
"**programmatically**: you build a map from the world, plan a path from the "
"robot's state to its goal, and (optionally) let the robot follow it with a "
"`dash` behavior or your own controller."
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 内置了基于栅格和基于采样的路径规划器，用于在占据地图上计算无碰撞路径。"
"规划器以**编程方式**使用：你从世界构建地图，规划一条从机器人当前状态到目标的"
"路径，并（可选）让机器人用 `dash` 行为或你自己的控制器去跟随它。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:5
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:7
msgid "Every planner follows the same four-step workflow:"
msgstr "每个规划器都遵循相同的四步流程："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:9
msgid ""
"**Build the map**: `env.get_map(resolution=...)` returns the occupancy grid "
"the planner searches (`resolution` is the planning cell size in meters)."
msgstr ""
"**构建地图** —— `env.get_map(resolution=...)` 返回规划器搜索所用的占据栅格"
"（`resolution` 是规划单元的尺寸，单位为米）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:10
msgid ""
"**Create the planner**: instantiate one planner from "
"`irsim.lib.path_planners`."
msgstr "**创建规划器** —— 从 `irsim.lib.path_planners` 实例化一个规划器。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:11
msgid ""
"**Plan**: `planner.planning(start, goal)` returns a trajectory (list of `[x, "
"y]` points), or `None` if no path is found."
msgstr ""
"**规划** —— `planner.planning(start, goal)` 返回一条轨迹（`[x, y]` 点的列"
"表），若找不到路径则返回 `None`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:12
msgid ""
"**Draw / follow**: `env.draw_trajectory(trajectory)` overlays the path; feed "
"it to a controller to follow it."
msgstr ""
"**绘制 / 跟随** —— `env.draw_trajectory(trajectory)` 叠加显示路径；将其传给控"
"制器即可跟随。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:14
msgid ""
"The start and goal come from the scene: `env.get_robot_state()` and "
"`env.get_robot_info().goal`."
msgstr ""
"起点和目标来自场景：`env.get_robot_state()` 与 `env.get_robot_info().goal`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_path_planning.md:16
msgid "Supported algorithms"
msgstr "支持的算法"

